</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_250" id="124v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Graf <expan>Lewpold<ex>en</ex></expan>, lantgrafen czum Leuhtemberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Dankwart Pirker,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie daz ir in gefangen habt.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        gnade der venknüsse ledig sag. Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. Und het ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> oder
                            <expan>dhein<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> czu
                                <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> icht <expan>czusprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt von <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> slewnigs
                                <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des
                        ermant werden. Und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> des
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedig
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica<ex>m</ex></expan> quasimodo
                            <expan>ge<ex>n</ex>iti</expan>.</ab>
</div>
